<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA23">
<l>piṟaiyum puṉalu maṉalaravuñ cūṭu</l>
<l>miṟaiva remakkiraṅkā rēṉuṅ - kaṟaimiṭaṟṟa</l>
<l>ventaiyārk kāṭpaṭṭē meṉṟeṉ ṟirukkumē</l>
<l>yentaiyā vuḷḷa mitu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if the lord who wears the crescent, the flood</l>
<l>and the fiery snake is not compassionate with us, this [is my] mind,</l>
<l>that, as our father, keeps saying “we are servants</l>
<l>of our father with the black throat”.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
